ghost.objects

Class Ghost

  • java.lang.Object
    • ghost.objects.Moving
      • ghost.objects.Ghost
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Ambusher, Chaser, Ignorant, Whim

    public abstract class Ghost
extends Moving
    The ghost class is a moving object, and unlike the player, moves on its own. It extends from Moving.

      • Ghost

        public Ghost(int x,
             int y,
             processing.core.PImage image,
             int movementSpeed)
        The Ghost constructor, calls the super constructor to set the current position, and the image. The frightened sprite is set to null initially, and the ghosts start in Scatter mode. Stores the home location and sets the current position as the recent intersection parameter.
